  <brief_title>Concentration of Ampicillin / Sulbactam and Amoxicillin / Clavulanic Acid in the Blood During Renal Replacement Therapy in Longterm Renal Replacement Therapy Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multiple-dose Pharmacokinetics of Ampicillin / Sulbactam and Amoxicillin / Clavulanic Acid During Haemodialysis in Longterm Haemodialysis Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
