  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study will be conducted to investigate the pharmacokinetics of ampicillin / sulbactam and
      amoxicillin/clavulanic acid during intermittent haemodialysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
